IBVA_MIDI_MAX Manual (PC & Mac Compatible)


1. Once you have live brainwave being received into IBVA navigate to the BrainNDJVJ tab.

2. Click on Brain rhythm MIDI setup.

3. Activate the ON MIDI out check box.

4. Toggle on Active Brain Data Input.

5. Select to Max 1 in the MIDI Out port.

6. In the IBVA_MIDI_MAX patch double click on the midiin a object. 

7. Select to Max 1 and MIDI data will start appearing for each of the channels. 
